<div class='communityQuestion'>
<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/630759-in-chapter-6-towards-the-end-of-the">In Chapter 6, towards the end of the chapter, they refer to &quot;Andersen&#39;s Well.&quot; I tried searching for an explanation but couldn&#39;t find anything. What oh what is meant by Andersen&#39;s Well???

Thank you!!!</a>
</div>
<div class='communityQAFooter questionFooter'>
<ul class='questionFooterActions'>
<li class='footerItem like'>
<span class='likeItContainer' id='like_container_community_question_630759'><a id="like_count_community_question_630759" rel="nofollow" href="/rating/voters/630759?resource_type=CommunityQuestion"><span class="likesCount">2 likes</span></a>&nbsp;&middot;&nbsp;<a rel="nofollow" class="jsLike like_it" href="https://www.goodreads.com/user/new?remember=true&amp;return_url=%2Fbook%2Fshow%2F4796.The_Winter_of_Our_Discontent">like</a></span>

