      <div class=" clearFloats bigBox"><div class="h2Container gradientHeaderContainer"><h2 class="brownBackground"><a href="/work/quotes/2359336-the-winter-of-our-discontent">Quotes from The Winter of Our...</a></h2></div><div class="bigBoxBody"><div class="bigBoxContent containerWithHeaderContent">
